/// ## Filename=GetWeather.js ##

function _GetOnedayWeather() {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    var lat = map.get_center().latitude;
    var lon = map.get_center().longitude;
    var zoomlevel = map.get_zoomLevel();
    if (zoomlevel < 10) {
        $("#taskBar_weatherButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_WeatherButton_Text);
        return;
    }
    $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: "./WeatherHandler.ashx",
        dataType: "text",
        data: "lat=" + lat + "&lon=" + lon,
        success: function (msg, status) {
            if (msg == "") {
                $("#taskBar_weatherButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_WeatherButton_Text);
            }
            else {
                $("#taskBar_weatherButtonText").text(msg);
            }
        },
        error: function () {
            $("#taskBar_weatherButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_WeatherButton_Text);
        }
    });
}

function _InitWeatherObtain() {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    if (map != null) {
        _GetOnedayWeather();
        map.attachEvent(map.get_map(), "viewchangeend", _GetOnedayWeather);
    }
}
/// ## Endfile=GetWeather.js ##

/// ## Filename=ChainHotel.js ##
function _GetHotelInfo(query, fromHome) {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    var lat = map.get_center().latitude;
    var lon = map.get_center().longitude;
    $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: "./hotels.ashx?q=" + encodeURIComponent(query) + "&r=e",
        data: "lat=" + lat + "&lon=" + lon,
        async: false,
        timeout: 2000,
        success: function (data) {
            VEShell.App.openHotel(data);
        }
    });
}

function ShowMoreZones() {
    var container = $('#MSVE_morezone_container');
    container.html($('#zoneMoreList').html());
    container.css('top', $('#100000').position().top + 25);
    container.css('left', $('#100000').position().left + 2);
    container.css('display', 'block');
}
function HideMoreZones() {
    var container = $('#MSVE_morezone_container');
    container.css('display', 'none');
}

function ShowMoreBrands() {
    var container = $('#MSVE_morebrand_container');
    container.html($('#brandMoreList').html());
    container.css('top', $('#100000_brandid').position().top + 25);
    container.css('left', $('#100000_brandid').position().left + 2);
    container.css('display', 'block');
}
function HideMoreBrands() {
    var container = $('#MSVE_morebrand_container');
    container.css('display', 'none');
}
/// ## Endfile=ChainHotel.js ##

/// ## Filename=GetAirQuality.js ##

function _GetAirQuality() {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    var lat = map.get_center().latitude;
    var lng = map.get_center().longitude;
    var zoomlevel = map.get_zoomLevel();
    var cityID;
    if (zoomlevel < 10) {
        $("#taskBar_airQualityButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_AirQualityButton_Text);
        return;
    }
    $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: "./AirQualityHandler.ashx",
        dataType: "json",
        data: "lat=" + lat + "&lng=" + lng + "&scope=l",
        success: function (msg) {
            if (msg != null) {
                $("#taskBar_airQualityButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_AirQualityButton_Text+": " + msg["desc"]);
            }
            else {
                $("#taskBar_airQualityButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_AirQualityButton_Text);
            }

        },
        error: function () {
            $("#taskBar_airQualityButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_AirQualityButton_Text);
        }

    });
}

function _InitAirQualityObtain() {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    if (map != null) {
        _GetAirQuality();
        map.attachEvent(map.get_map(), "viewchangeend", _GetAirQuality);
    }
}
/// ## Endfile=GetAirQuality.js ##

/// ## Filename=GetCurrentCity.js ##

function _GetCurrentCity() {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    var lat = map.get_center().latitude;
    var lng = map.get_center().longitude;
    var zoomlevel = map.get_zoomLevel();
    if (zoomlevel < 5) {
        $("#taskBar_setCityButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_CurrentCityButton_Text);
        return;
    }
    $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: "./SubwayCityHandler.ashx",
        dataType: "text",
        data: "lat=" + lat + "&lng=" + lng + "&lvl=" + zoomlevel + "&scope=cc",
        success: function (msg) {
            if (msg != null && msg != '' && msg != 'other') {
                $("#taskBar_setCityButtonText").text(msg);
            }
            else if (msg == null || msg == '') {
                $("#taskBar_setCityButtonText").text(VEShellResources.ShellResource.l_CurrentCityButton_Text);
            }
        }
    });
}

function _InitCurrentCityObtain() {
    var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
    if (map != null) {
        _GetCurrentCity();
        map.attachEvent(map.get_map(), "viewchangeend", _GetCurrentCity);
    }
}

var VE_SubwayCityWidget = new function () {
    this.openSubwayCity = function () {
        var map = VEShell.App.get_map();
        var lat = map.get_center().latitude;
        var lon = map.get_center().longitude;
        var zoomlevel = map.get_zoomLevel();
        var openuri = null;
        $.ajax({
            async: false,
            type: "POST",
            url: "./SubwayCityHandler.ashx",
            dataType: "text",
            data: "lat=" + lat + "&lon=" + lon + "&scope=sc" + "&lvl=" + zoomlevel,
            success: function (data) {
                if (data != null && data != "") {
                    openuri = "/subway/" + data + "?FORM=MAPMTR";
                }
                else {                    
                    __doPostBack('subwayCityWidget', 'SubwayCity_Opening');
                }
            }
        });
        if (openuri != null) { window.open(openuri); }
    };
};
